; Coverage test for parser.cc L415
; Tests a trailing comma in a function argument list, followed by
; a closing parenthesis. The parser sees COMMA then RPAREN and breaks
; out of the comma expression loop.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --display 'justify(amount, 10,)'
24-Jan-01 Test                  Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
end test
